.0] } { Blunder. Bd2 was best. } 26... Rxb3 { [%eval 0.0] } { 这次我抓住了机会。 } 27. axb3 { [%eval 0.0] } 27... Rb8 { [%eval -0.03] } { 这样白方的后翼多兵冲不动了。 } 28. Rb1?? { [%eval -2.02] } { Blunder. Rc2 was best. } 28... a5 { [%eval -1.91] } { 这个时候我发现我居然吃回兵了。不过我想着的还是保底和棋,没有意识到实际上已经大优了。 } 29. Bc1 { [%eval -2.06] } 29... a4 { [%eval -1.99] } 30. b4 { [%eval -1.94] } 30... Rc8 { [%eval -2.05] } 31. Bb2? { [%eval -4.24] } { 这样反而变成我多兵。 } 31... Bxb2 { [%eval -4.23] } 32. Rxb2 { [%eval -4.22] } 32... Rxc4 { [%eval -4.21] } 33. g3 { [%eval -4.51] } 33... Rd4 { [%eval -4.29] } 34. b5 { [%eval -4.65] } 34... Rxd5 { [%eval -3.93] } 35. b6 { [%eval -4.88] } 35... Kc8 { [%eval -5.04] } 36. Rb4 { [%eval -5.26] } 36... Kb7?? { [%eval -0.59] } { Blunder. Ra5 was best. } { 车兵残局不熟练导致的。我并不知道 3v3 + 通路兵什么时候能赢。不过 Ra5 确实赢得简明。 } 37. Rxa4 { [%eval -0.64] } 37... Kxb6 { [%eval -0.83] } 38. Rc4?! { [%eval -1.65] } { Inaccuracy. Ra1 was best. } 38... Rc5 { [%eval -1.33] } 39. Rd4 { [%eval -1.17] } 39... Kc6 { [%eval -1.2] } 40. Kg2 { [%eval -1.52] } 40... d5 { [%eval -1.47] } 41. Ra4 { [%eval -1.48] } 41... Kd6?! { [%eval -0.67] } { Inaccuracy. Kb6 was best. } 42. Ra8?! { [%eval -1.4] } { Inaccuracy. Kf3 was best. } { 这种局面弱方最重要的应该是把王的位置变得积极一些。 } 42... Rc6 { [%eval -1.14] } 43. Rh8? { [%eval -2.63] } { Mistake. Kf3 was best. } 43... h5 { [%eval -2.4] } 44. Kf3 { [%eval -2.66] } 44... Ke5 { [%eval -2.57] } 45. Re8+?! { [%eval -3.7] } { Inaccuracy. Ke2 was best. } 45... Kd4? { [%eval -1.93] } { Mistake. Re6 was best. } { 这里 ...Re6 隔开王应该直接简单胜了。 } 46. Ra8? { [%eval -3.81] } { Mistake. Re1 was best. } 46... Kd3 { [%eval -3.53] } 47. h4?! { [%eval -4.77] } { Inaccuracy. Ra3+ was best. } 47... d4 { [%eval -4.66] } 48. Ra1 { [%eval -4.88] } 48... Re6 { [%eval -4.6] } { 现在隔开了。以下就没有技术含量了。 } 49. Rd1+?! { [%eval -6.29] } { Inaccuracy. g4 was best. } 49... Kc3 { [%eval -5.75] } 50. Rc1+ { [%eval -6.55] } 50... Kd2 { [%eval -6.12] } 51. Ra1 { [%eval -5.89] } 51... d3 { [%eval -6.32] } 52. Ra2+ { [%eval -7.43] } 52... Kc1 